{"type":"message","id":"6cbb7141","parentId":"13128495","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:27:30.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8a2701571c3c46b3875bc5ad","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": 1,\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9b911fa3-7f30-42ae-ae4b-a3492945a941\",\n      \"agentId\": \"fox-smarthome\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"每日早晨天气播报（主卧）- 狐狸智能管家\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773367443169,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773963055991,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"30 7 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"现在是早上 7:30，请帮小王子做每日天气播报。\\n\\n步骤：\\n1. 用 web_fetch 获取广州南沙今天天气：https://wttr.in/南沙，广州？format=j1\\n2. 根据返回数据，组装一段简洁亲切的中文天气播报，包含：今天天气状况、温度范围、降水/湿度建议（如需要带伞等）。语气温暖，适合早晨。\\n3. 用 exec 调用 Home Assistant TTS 将播报文字播放到主卧音箱：\\n   curl -s -X POST \\\"$HA_URL/api/services/tts/speak\\\" \\\\\\n     -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $HA_TOKEN\\\" \\\\\\n     -H \\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\" \\\\\\n     -d '{\\\"entity_id\\\": \\\"tts.home_assistant_cloud\\\", \\\"media_player_entity_id\\\": \\\"media_player.xiaomi_lx06_46d3_play_control\\\", \\\"message\\\": \\\"<播报文字>\\\", \\\"language\\\": \\\"zh-CN\\\"}'\\n4. 完成后简短回报播报内容。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"user:ou_0671c63ec5781695e9ca1ec20c78f94e\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774049400000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773963000025,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 55966,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f0d5558e-e2ab-4ab3-a2a1-686f6a007ba9\",\n      \"agentId\": \"fox-smarthome\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"入户门监控（每 15 分钟）- 狐狸智能管家\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773367582786,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773710268839,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 900000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773710268839\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"请检查入户门传感器，看过去 15 分钟内有没有人来。\\n\\n步骤：\\n1. 用 exec 查询最近 15 分钟的历史：\\n```\\ncurl -s \\\"$HA_URL/api/history/period/$(date -u -d '15 minutes ago' +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S.000Z)?filter_entity_id=binary_sensor.lumi_cn_719859620_acn001_contact_state_p_2_1&minimal_response=true\\\" -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $HA_TOKEN\\\" | jq '.[0] | [.[] | select(.state == \\\"on\\\") | .last_changed]'\\n```\\n2. 如果返回列表不为空（有 `on` 状态记录），说明有人开过门，用 message tool 通知群聊（target=\\\"chat:oc_b23350a0074cc1db4fd6176331127182\\\"）：\\\"🚪 过去 15 分钟有人来过！门开时间：<时间列表，转换为北京时间>\\\"\\n3. 如果没有开门记录，不做任何通知，直接回复 NO_NOTIFY 即可。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773707233137,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 32912,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 10,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"rate_limit\",\n        \"lastDeliveryError\": \"⚠️ API rate limit reached. Please try again later.\",\n        \"lastError\": \"⚠️ API rate limit reached. Please try again later.\"\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-1111-2222-3333-444455556666\",\n      \"agentId\": \"fox-smarthome\",\n     