{"type":"message","id":"41fccd45","parentId":"131543b5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:28:01.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经成功将备份目录中的定时任务配置文件复制到当前工程，并创建了相关的文档说明。让我向用户报告完成情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已完成定时任务迁移\n\n**操作结果：**\n1. ✅ 创建了 `cron` 目录\n2. ✅ 复制了 `jobs.json` 定时任务配置文件（22.9KB）\n3. ✅ 创建了 `CRON.md` 文档，说明定时任务管理\n\n**定时任务统计：**\n- 总任务数：16 个\n- 启用任务：13 个\n- 禁用任务：3 个（原因：API rate limit / 账户余额不足）\n\n**主要任务类型：**\n- 🌤️ 天气播报（3个）\n- 🧹 清洁任务（3个）\n- 🪟 窗帘控制（2个）\n- 💡 灯光控制（2个）\n- 🔍 检查任务（3个）\n\n**查看方式：**\n```bash\ncat /home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-smarthome/cron/jobs.json\n```\n\n**文档位置：**\n- `./cron/jobs.json` - 定时任务配置\n- `./CRON.md` - 定时任务管理说明"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":2271,"output":318,"cacheRead":27224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29813,"cost":{"input":0.00020438999999999999,"output":0.00009222,"cacheRead":0.00122508,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00152169}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773991678118}}
